import React from 'react'; import carsData from '../ContentFiles/Cars.json'; // Adjust the path as necessary const Cars = () => { return (

OUR CARS

{carsData.map((car, index) => (

{car.model}

{car.year}

CHASIS:

{car.chasis}

Power Unit:

{car.powerunit}

Weight:

{car.weight}

Achievement:

{car.achievement}

Competition Placement:

{car.placement}

))}
); } export default Cars;
